import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Account } from '../../components/Account'
import { accountWithBalance,
        accountWithoutBalance, 
        accountWithoutAddress, accountPicker} from './accountVariants'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"account"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#account"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Account`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"account-with-address-and-balance"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#account-with-address-and-balance"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Account with address and balance`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __code={`<Account account={accountWithBalance} showAccountPicker={accountPicker} />`} __scope={{props,Account,accountWithBalance,accountWithoutBalance,accountWithoutAddress,accountPicker}}>
    <Account account={accountWithBalance} 
             showAccountPicker={accountPicker} />
</Playground> 
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"account-with-address-but-no-balance"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#account-with-address-but-no-balance"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Account with address but no balance`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<Account account={accountWithoutBalance} showAccountPicker={accountPicker} />`} __scope={{props,Account,accountWithBalance,accountWithoutBalance,accountWithoutAddress,accountPicker}}>
    <Account account={accountWithoutBalance}
             showAccountPicker={accountPicker} />
</Playground> 
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"account-with-no-address"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#account-with-no-address"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Account with no address`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __code={`<Account account={accountWithoutAddress} showAccountPicker={accountPicker} />`} __scope={{props,Account,accountWithBalance,accountWithoutBalance,accountWithoutAddress,accountPicker}}>
    <Account account={accountWithoutAddress}
             showAccountPicker={accountPicker} />
</Playground> 
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties-table"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#properties-table"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Properties Table`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Account} /></MDXTag>
